OL,3,CMan arrested in rape investigation
OL,5,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,6,Fof rape in connection with a serious
OL,7,Fsexual assault in Bristol.
OL,9,FAvon and Somerset Police is
OL,10,Finvestigating after a woman was raped
OL,11,Fin the Assembly Rooms Lane area at
OL,12,Faround 3.05am on Sunday 29 March.
OL,14,FThe force said two other men have been
OL,15,Freleased under investigation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
