CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1775571065
OL,3,CMan arrested in rape investigation
OL,5,FDet Insp Christian Vogler, who is
OL,6,Fleading the investigation, said: "The
OL,7,Fvictim remains our main priority and
OL,8,Fwe are working hard to try and provide
OL,9,Fher with answers about what happened
OL,10,Fand hold those responsible to account.
OL,12,F"We continue to provide her with the
OL,13,Fsupport she needs and update her on
OL,14,Fthe progress of our enquiries," he
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,17,FAvon and Somerset Police is urging
OL,18,Fpeople not to speculate online as it
OL,19,Fcould impact the investigation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
